{"title":"水","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":10,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从水的无涯天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来人的初祖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肌肉的山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪射水的晶莹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乳水长流的生命泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发育大脑肺腑四肢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背负青天水之滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色亮眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"视线水透明……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人的母亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗怎样长高？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器怎样转动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜怎样出太阳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天宇怎样添新星？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间天上，每页史诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有水的淘洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水的滋润，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水的深恩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水的爱情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧不尽，斩不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩荡坚定；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手儿掬，云儿亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温柔轻盈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼洒水的珍珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族水的盛大节日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗涤临盆婴孩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由水开始人生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一清如水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水的明镜多公平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美的清廉，丑的贪婪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接触水顿时现形。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流水不腐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进穿透铁甲钢盾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"律法威严制裁腐恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪波涌起，丧身灭顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欺山莫欺水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玷污水就是自杀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自我放逐到沙漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头发起火，枯焦自焚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁胆敢把清流变祸水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必定害了自己害儿孙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴水能鉴今古，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴水有爱有憎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴水能教天平倾斜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴水可以杀人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮映水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮更媚光喜人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵映水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵更美艳新颖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像鱼儿痴痴恋着水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恋着人的母亲。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}